Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:04.57,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:07.84,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽约的话下得更夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.37,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是挺怀念的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.74,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从离开那个城市以后很久没看过雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:34.96,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来是那样想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:37.00,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.19,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方也确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:47.76,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种心情下有个很适合的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:49.60,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:51.87,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来提个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.75,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.87,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:02.38,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:07.23,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外的价值全都是感伤的蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:10.80,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱就是上帝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:11.55,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.24,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比上帝更加有种的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:15.28,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.78,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除开这个 你还想追求什么价值啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:23.95,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我还是小屁孩到处乱爬的粪坑里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:28.20,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么上帝还是爱都长期缺货
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:32.77,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不懂事的时候 我也曾经对着上帝痛哭过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.54,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 相信那种鬼东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:42.18,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只到我无辜被巡警打个半死的那个夜晚为止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:46.47,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由仅仅是因为我住在贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.19,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有力量 没有上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:52.40,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为中国母猴子的小鬼到底还有什么能依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:54.57,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.94,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:00.99,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾起你痛苦的回忆了呢 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:01.74,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:10.59,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有能比被同伴当作妓女更令人心酸的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:14.73,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你要是还想跟我谈正常位的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.80,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不再是我同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.65,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:21.55,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.75,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带Cutlass虽然有点遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:28.07,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是带在身上三秒就能让这店关门大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.80,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 双亲不是还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.23,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少去联络一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.18,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有弄脏手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:38.90,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要见就趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.25,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干这行总有一天会再也见不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.46,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来你那也是普通的一家人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.66,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还有回去的价值吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:53.02,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不用偷不用杀活到现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:00.69,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我就去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.96,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 快给我去 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.71,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.45,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不会等很久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.59,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我喝完这罐为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:17.34,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就会离开 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.03,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.55,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里看都一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:26.57,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.44,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的贫民窟也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:32.50,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jack McCall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.69,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威鲁·比尔的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.95,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能打得过我简吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.03,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.27,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇 被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:49.36,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会那样倒下的只有电影和TV秀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.73,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 真的是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:53.88,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是会突然全身没力倒下的 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.51,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我示范给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.03,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.62,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看起来好像很逊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.67,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的时候就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.28,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能让你死得帅不帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.05,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.90,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到父母了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.19,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是回了一趟家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:28.15,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 结果还是没见着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:29.50,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:31.18,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.24,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.19,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不回去啊 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.92,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么适合这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.35,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.70,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.37,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薇 果然我还是不能不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.99,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能陪我一起去那女孩那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.47,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我犯傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.98,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想你和他们是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:04.01,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们可是和他们的死敌是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.56,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩和我们不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:06.14,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.24,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:07.64,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.14,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这里也不是罗阿那普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.36,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.71,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不一样了 洛克 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:17.06,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经是这边的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.88,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后大姐头也准备用罗阿那普拉那套做法处理这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.72,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.97,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.54,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我求你了 洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.65,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是分水岭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:33.14,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是越过了这里 没有任何能回头的路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:37.36,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游览券卖光了 班车也不会再走这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.80,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话你懂了没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:42.15,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.05,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.02,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.08,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 刚才的话忘掉吧 洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:56.01,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了重要的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.00,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这我是你的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.17,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的使命只是保护你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.15,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是干涉你的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.12,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会陪你去的 Master
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.60,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生不好好享受会吃亏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.64,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.56,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.68,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一不小心就
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:43.74,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诱惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.48,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非太遥远而触碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.01,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一直都混浊不堪的空气中活到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.94,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不懂得怎么在其它地方生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:58.30,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连这都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.14,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.32,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且别回头 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.21,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的噩梦也该是时候醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.79,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薇 你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.05,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.25,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在和你相遇的那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:21.08,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果罗阿那普拉是活死人的国度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.03,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是活人的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.80,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太过熟悉的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.21,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也把这事给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.21,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对死人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.62,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这明明是如同梦幻一般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:36.38,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是为了回到这里而回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.84,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了忘记这里而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.95,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了正视至今发生了的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.42,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.23,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.85,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔的话一年前就后悔够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.50,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足的只是觉悟而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:55.09,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在好像已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.62,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.90,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前那姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.14,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.02,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 再让我看看之前那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.10,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是把罐子打飞的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.05,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}Well Rock
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.05,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.23,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}Put on a show for them Revy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.23,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们见识见识 莉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.65,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}all right
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.65,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.46,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是 什么枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.12,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:24.16,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}This here's Beretta M92 custom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:24.16,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伯莱塔 M92 改装版
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.77,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}The Praiyachat Sword Cutlass speial
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.77,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特制的 Praiyachat Sword Cutlass
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.80,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}Now watch those cans carefully you brats
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.80,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在给我好好看着那些罐 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.72,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}Those cans watch in close OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.72,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看着那些罐 懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.94,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}Your mommy is waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.94,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们老妈在等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.67,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1000)\fs50}Now go home you kids
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.67,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回家 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.53,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海湾的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.55,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一尊像这样闪闪发光的佛像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.13,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而却以凄惨的姿态伫立在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.08,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其背后孕育着的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:20.92,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶的港湾 罗阿那普拉